Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIN-KAWASAKI (TENTATIVE)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your T-shirts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIN-KAWASAKI (TENTATIVE)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're also selling towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you there was no point\Nin trying to sell merch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why even make merch if we\Nhaven't even settled on a name yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just... I thought maybe\Nwe could get a leg up on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What, like a football team\Nselling ahead of season?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we become famous enough, maybe we really can go {\i1}premier{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you optimistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you spacing out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\i1}Thank you for showing up!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll be supporting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hope to see you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... Rupa-san sure is popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, we gotta get the\Nband's name sorted out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right...\N- You have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,6: PUT A NAME ON IT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- A concert...?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Someone that I owe a lot to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}offered me a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where's the venue?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Suwa, in Nagano prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is to head there the night before the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And to come back right after.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hectic schedule,\Nso I can manage on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since you're busy studying, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?\NOur coordination is still a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it fine? The more experience we get...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so, Rupa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- In conclusion: let's go!\N- Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do\Nabout our band name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}SOMEDAY LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be clear, if we stay as\N"Shin-Kawasaki", I'm seriously quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just as serious about\Nbeing professional after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does Momoka-san think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told her we were\Nserious about going pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Like a Cold War stalemate, huh?\N- How can you say that with a straight face...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san has been giving Nina\Nthe cold shoulder, alright. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where did the lizard go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,GECKO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She tends to hide away\Nwhenever she's not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's she like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's got a problem,\Nwhy doesn't she just tell us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop shouting!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't blame her for being mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Given how Nina just does whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this whole thing was {\i1}your{\i0} plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teehee!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as a warning, but if you three can't\Nwork as a band, we're pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We ain't got the time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note, what name\Ndo you think would best fit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A ragtag team of misfits like ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't you have any ideas?\N- Huh? Why you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! If you ask something,\Nyou should answer first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My name's a little\Nembarrassing though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you all say it at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, on the count of three then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Undine! {\i0}    - {\i1}Dream Girl!{\i0}     - {\i1}Chokolate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Undine! {\i0}    - {\i1}Dream Girl!{\i0}     - {\i1}Chokolate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "Chocolate", with a "K", {\i1}Chokolate{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've seen it coming....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A real Kumamoto bumpkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cheesy it's giving me diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What even was yours? {\i1}Undine{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way more cringe than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both cringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what did you come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Dream Girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined it'd be this\Nhard to agree on a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear nothing's good\Nenough for you, Subaru....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} - THE NINAZ!!  - Village People Kawasaki\N- Heavenly Cow Voice  - Summers Ladies\N- Nina's Nakama  - Bukubuku\N- Fluffy {\s1}Totoro{\s0}Tororo  - TanTanTanmen\N- {\s1}What's on tomorrow's test?{\s0}  - Mermaids\N-Hamburg Set Meal   - {\u1}You Reap What You {\s1}Study{\s0}!!{\u0}\N-Gamadas  - Sekarashicar\N- Roku-on! {\i1}(sounds cool!!){\i0} - Katsudon! Gyudon! DON!!\N- ADAMAS - Birthday - BEEG KAWASAKI\N- rAMEN tsukeMEN - Short (BIG) Cake - OrangeLemon&Mikan\N- Adolescent Salad Dressing {\i1}(I'm hungry now){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, that's my line~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"You picked the name yet?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, and we wasted a whole day on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Late as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,O... onee-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've let me\Nknow you were coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to surprise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't expecting\Nyou to get home this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I was... busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh? With a {\i1}boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're\Ndoing a sketchy job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A band.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A band.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A band?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You?! Wait. You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pics or it didn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... no way. You're the vocalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What we call Rock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock 'n' Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains your plummeting grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'd expect a school to call the family\Nif their kid starts skipping classes all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Those rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful that I convinced\Nyour dad to come in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I left that home. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But once you tell him that,\Nyou won't be able to return again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I also think your father was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW TO RAISE A CHILD 101
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For a professor renown for\Nhis publications on education...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...He couldn't stand the thought\Nof his daughter not going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he ended up\Nhurting you in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also understand\Nwhere he was coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't escalated the\Nsituation with the bullying,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The school would've owed you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And with your grades,\Nyou could've gotten into a good university.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's... not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why ran away\Nto enter university all on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet look where that's got you,\Nand you still say you won't come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As I feared, not even I can defend that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}SOME DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we've got practice\Ntomorrow morning, so let's get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the baggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This, this, and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave the rest behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to learn to travel lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking the Chuo Expressway,\Nright? For the tolls--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Manual? That's rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to borrow it from an acquaintance,\Nso I guess beggars can't be choosers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How you do this again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in favor of switching drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very good at driving, Rupa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to drive a lot for my last job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you wanna do it in one go?\NWe can take breaks, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my driving really {\i1}that{\i0} terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get tired I'll just pull over to a gas\Nstation, so feel free to rest if you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeh? But we finally got time\Nwith the five of us together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, wanna play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask a question, and if everyone\Ncan relate, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For example... I prefer cats over dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh? I would've never guesssed\Nyou were a dog person, Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The say people who act like\Na sour{\i1}puss{\i0} tend to like dogs more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have almost no friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gottem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Game will be over in a second like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... who here hates my driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}DANGOZAKA SERVICE AREA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back,\Nso hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Woah, it's packed!\N- Cut it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rock, Paper, Scissors!\N- How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How much was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I pick the wrong one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...Nah, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan... why did you drop out of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can't ask anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have the luxury\Nto waste my time there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents were never there for me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd have to survive\Non my own after I graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When she brought other men home,\Nshe felt like a whole other creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing her like that,\Nit flipped a switch in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not rare for indie artists\Nto start before they even graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sooner I run away, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I fled to Tokyo, formed a band,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,School was taking up too much of my time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When you don't have anyone you can rely on\Nanymore, you have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa lost her mother in an accident, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...She said she felt the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I never gave it any thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a big smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san, Tomo-chan, smile a bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Say {\i1}"cheese please"{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We look like idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,WELCOME, TO THE LAND OF SUWA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we can't afford a hotel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm boiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,TOMORROW: SUWA FIREWORKS FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're getting somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? We're all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't you two the newbies here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We all suck equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, Subaru-chan,\Nyour neck is... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Sleeping in a car ain't easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your new band, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Momo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Indeed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say you're {\i1}great{\i0}, \Nbut you're not half bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies. We will try our best\Nto not spoil the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. The one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your sticker's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}DIAMOND DUST
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just me or is she...\Nlike a whole other person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe this is how she always used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's okay, could we do this final song together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that okay? \N- I'd be honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to play with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's why I invited you to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... ehm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're at it, why don't we have a quick {\i1}session{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Session{\i0}?\N- Practicing together, she means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the vocalist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waving goodbye to melodies of past{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until the day we may meet again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if that may mean{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I'll forget{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm an adult once again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- So?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you sing it?\N- Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decided then. I'll go fetch the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's a great singer, isn't she?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first landed in Tokyo,\NI got to see her playing live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just an extra for the opening act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet she sang her heart out\Nlike her life depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought: "Ah... this is Rock!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm glad that I can perform\Nwith her for my final concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After tomorrow, it's over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you even saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't have the heart to\Nsupport this band... to go pro again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My music isn't the type of stuff\Nthat makes it in the world of pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... when you said you\Nliked my music, it made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm grateful that you stood up\Nfor me. Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,YAKITORI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Never would've thought you'd become\Nthis much of a drinker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa-san, you can hold your alcohol too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragging others into her alcoholism...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me we're gonna have to drag\Nher fat ass again... Ugh, I can already envision it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to keep it together tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe our customers that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- I get it...\N- What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are we arguing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That aside, what type of\Nmusic do you like, Mine-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine-san, have you ever thought of quitting music?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone enjoys\Nhaving to make that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you do something,\Nthe more you realize your skill with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail once, it's easy to chalk it as bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But fail twice, and we already resign\Nourselves that we've got no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you stop believing... that you're any good anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to keep believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But the taller we set our hopes,\Nthe more painful the scars from the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we love music so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... not get scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, I sometimes\Ncan't sleep or eat over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the life of turning your\Ntrue passion into your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was studying music,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about becoming a teacher\Nand just sing for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept telling myself\Nthat was the smart choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've probably forgotten already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You... forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that the stage is the only place\Nwhere I can truly express myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I won't stress over if it's too scary or difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's probably why, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you STINK!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you sayjing... I havennn drunk a drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked you can lie {\i1}this{\i0} shamelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh jus ssshut up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always, always, always, always,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- See ya.\N- alWAAAAAAAYSSS...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you lisssening??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Momoka-san for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't dump us with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor fair, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, which way is the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it, I've got it, I've got it! I finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,KAMISUWA KAICHO VENUE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coming up is a band that's dear to me, so stay tuned!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh by the way, what are we even naming ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you picked one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to settle it over dinner, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Shin-Kawasaki is... ugh, fine, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good evening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}We are...\N{\i0}- That sly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uhm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TOGEARI TOGENASHI\N(THORNLESS THORNS)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}TOGENASHI TOGEARI!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, same as my t-shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Spring, we started this\Nband kinda out of nowhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not really sure why I did it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or why I'm even singing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... it's fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the first time in my life,\NI've become passionate about something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My life... all changed\Nthanks to this one song.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It became my strength to keep moving forward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I want to prove that song was not wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That this song can move hearts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to tell people how incredible it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subaru-chan, Rupa-san,\NTomo-chan, and Momoka-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure that we can rely on each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'll try my best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared...\Nbut I want to believe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm gonna...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough monologues!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess of an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing quite like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scarred, forever, my mind and body are fragmented{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}\NPassion and cruelty go round and round in my head{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I plunge into the city, full of lies, it just makes me sick{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Within the stench and the noise,\NI cry out alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing is happening. How are you doing today?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you stop saying such dumb things?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That creepy voice echoes in my mind. While my tears keep flowing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You don't have to be afraid, so stop hiding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come and dance with me," you said{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to run away from this putrid world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to disperse{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Disperse, disperse, quietly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quietly, don't let me be alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like sorrow laid out in the bars of a song{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forever and ever and ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until love can be proven{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to believe that love is an emotion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could go insane{\i0}
